08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>扎威·阿什顿透露了她的未婚夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hiddleston">汤姆·希德勒斯顿</a>给她的关于为漫威工作的建议。</p><p>阿什顿在新片<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><em>《漫威》</em></a>中饰演达本，她的搭档曾在多部漫威作品中饰演洛基。</p><p>阿什顿告诉<em><a href="https://ew.com/movies/the-marvels-zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-villain-advice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《娱乐周刊》</a></em> ：“这引发了一些令人难以置信的对话，谈论他在这支球队十多年来的经历。”</p><p> “我们谈话的主要收获之一是：‘你投入漫威的东西，你就会得到回报。’”他说：“如果你怀着开放的心态和良好的职业道德进入这个领域，并且只想为粉丝提供令人惊叹的体验，那么你将在这些场景中获得令人惊叹的体验。”他确实以这种方式赋予了我力量。”</p><p>这位<em>《鲜肉》</em>明星补充道：“他还提出了一些非常好的实用建议，那就是：确保你有足够的拉链，可以穿着服装去洗手间。我现在意识到，这是一个非常好的建议。” </p><figure id="attachment_2879220" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2879220" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2879220" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230.jpg" alt="惊奇队长" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2879220" class="wp-caption-text"> Zawe Ashton 于 2020 年 2 月伦敦时装周。图片来源：Kirstin Sinclair/Getty Images</figcapti